'''Song-yâu-tshûn''' (上窰村,  Hiông-kóng [[Hak-kâ-fa]] piang-yîm : [sɔŋ<sub>53</sub> yau<sub>11</sub>] ) he [[Hiông-kóng]] sit-ngit yit-thiàu [[Hak-kâ]] tshûn-lo̍k, vi-é tshai  [[Sîn-kie]] [[Sî-kung-khî]] [[Pet-thâm-yúng]], fông-fi heu yí-kîn sṳ̀n-vì [[Hiông-kóng Fap-thin Kú-tsiak]] pin kói-tsok [[Mìn-siu̍k Vùn-vu̍t-kón]].
Song-yâu-tshûn he [[Sṳ̍p-kiú sṳ-ki]] chûng-ya̍p (yok [[1830-ngièn]]) yù Vòng siang ke Ha-kâ-ngìn kien-sat. Liá-ke tshûn-tsôn kien-tshai yit-ke kô-tshut thi-mien ke phiàng-thòi song.

